Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说　昨天的电视节目超有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯　你看了？　我也是　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　眼睛里进脏东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有生以来第一次体验到什么叫“蹑手蹑脚”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！甘草！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！甘草！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住！甘草！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大　大家的表情好像有点可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦　我们不是和平常一样面带微笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么奇怪的话啊　甘草
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么　我们的友情都不会破裂　不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们生气了...吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明全是那个诅咒的错...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　甘草君对黑白院会长的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“那个”做了“什么”是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　为什么被你说得那么猥琐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在真心不是开玩笑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草君才是　不要开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在认真地问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显胡闹的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果不这样的话　我好害怕　根本问不出口嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那个　小甘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　游王子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那个　其实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说自那以后...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天穿了紧身裤　所以没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就不是没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常明明是个奇葩小孩　经常露个肚脐什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这家伙一扯到内裤就这么...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是学生会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想见你所以就来了　奏同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下　会长你到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请像往常一样叫我“清罗”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大家面前害羞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　就到只有我们两人的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先来一下这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这种事　目的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛　甘草同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有喜欢过人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个先回答我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有喜欢过别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那当然是毫无疑问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样　在初中也很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有过被人告白的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？　确实是受欢迎来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我自己对别人产生这样的感情就...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我　为什么你要装作喜欢我的样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我着急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务本应该让那个孩子来完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　等下　会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦　裘可拉　没迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊　我先来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从早上就各种状况不断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎　怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有三个选项？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是在这种状况下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　不行了　只能选了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行　不能选雪平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是平常的游王子还好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的状态实在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就只剩下...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选项又出现了　所以只好稍微抱你一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　很难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话　能不能放开我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　希望您不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是讨厌奏对我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经超过了身体异常的范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能在二人独处的时候做　我会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘　裘可拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常敬慕奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏也非常疼爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间只有近似于友爱的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不存在大家想象的那种不健全行为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉..酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏　您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　你是何方来人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是裘可拉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道　但是你..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像恢复记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等　总之先来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说记忆恢复了是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对　是今天早上的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在地板上醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从床上掉下来的时候头部被摔得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此而产生了剧烈的头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　对正常活动没有什么影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是状况没有得到改善
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那记忆呢　什么时候怎么恢复的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是要恢复的前兆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于恢复记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还缺少某种最终的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　被奏　那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住的瞬间　身体发热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回过神来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就恢复记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏　之前的我一直丑态百出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我会努力一洗污名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我之前的无礼举动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等　等下等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说　之前的你不是裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你才是真的裘可拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　雪平　什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以把这当做是新型的情景扮演PLAY吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不...说实话我也没搞清状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回答也是情景中的选项吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么说得好像是在红灯区一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人　要延长时间可是要追加付费的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　雪平　你好像生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气？　被称为晴光学院微笑大魔人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可没有那种情感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个称号我可一次都没听过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我有的闪闪发光的纯粹感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前等待我的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限的幸福　永远的庄严　永恒的轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是两位的爱情表现呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　你说爱情表现什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱　爱情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　雪平　是你发出的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？　你的脸好像有点发红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羡慕　刚才的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　富良野同学和奏的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　我吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？　所以说你到底是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害　这真的是裘可拉做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　请用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢　好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让奏满意　我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘　裘可拉也吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　等奏用餐完毕后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃剩下的就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　那个食欲魔人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不　一起吃吧　好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　奏您这么说了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　一直被这样盯着我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　对　对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀　这个气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开　开电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂　为什么这个时间放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　对　对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才自己才说过不要盯着看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个气氛到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　这就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们神的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量效率非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要从食物那里摄取太多的营养
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　昨天为止　在你肚子里消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨量食物们到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　昨天之前的我不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个女孩子却那么贪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊没有　嘛　那个还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是裘可拉吃不了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　对不起　煮太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　这里面也有可以保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然扔了也...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　我会全部吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子难得为自己做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以随意剩下呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏　因为我的笨拙给你造成了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我协助你进食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　不不　这个实在有点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　又给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　啊　不是不是　拜拜拜　拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　果然比想的要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈　那那　这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我会自己吃的　好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能同意的话　那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　到底是什么回事　这个气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈　累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给您擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不　我没有拜托过那种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力帮您擦背的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁　屁股的部分放过我的话　那就太感激了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　没有拜托过你那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　前面的话　我怎么努力都没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拿来的色情漫画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情不用努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去　好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我拒绝擦屁股和前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以坏了奏的兴致吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那个　今天我已经自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗过身　身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再拜托你吧　好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗　那我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天一定哦　我先退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天都在震惊当中度过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有机会和你好好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了解一下你现在的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么　请允许我来说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先　我们神的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如其名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们主要是为了完成神大人下达的任务而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过去也曾勤勤恳恳的工作过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是某个时期我丧失了记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且人格也随之发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这以后就进入了懒惰期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天只知道玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了神发来的指令书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容是去甘草奏的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这时候不就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神搞不伦之恋怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被不伦恋对象的老婆喊作偷腥猫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到打击的神挺着肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲进家里闭门不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是有名的神的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,⑤偷腥猫　闭门不出事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这之后别的神匆忙来接手这个案件了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那个荒唐神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好你好我是神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就到了奏的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是甘草奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就在奏家里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边让脑浆继续坏掉一边狂吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着糜烂的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后今天　那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被奏抱着　记忆就恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说让事态变得麻烦的是那个家里蹲神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起　我对那边的事实关系还不太...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是关于轻浮神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上家里着蹲的前任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对诅咒的事情也没有把握得很详细
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是我接手　还不如说是让我收拾烂摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往我的脑内发送绝对选项
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我完成莫名其妙任务的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪魁祸首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起　关于那件事　详细的我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　没关系　至少我重新确认了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我所不知道的第三个神的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连神的详情都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能照顾奏的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也可以待在您身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉　啊　啊　可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶　这　这么高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀　糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说　刚才　你刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢...你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　奏对我怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额　不不　你突然让我说这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让绝对选项消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够做到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话　请从了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能请您和我接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕现在的裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论我做什么都不会拒绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是kiss还是做更进一步的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这个　裘可拉　不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然奏不从的话　那么就由我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊　对　对不起　没事吧　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛　等　等等啊裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想让绝对选项消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？　kiss就能让绝对选项消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉　这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我接吻就那么令你讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的　眼神还这么迷离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是能听进话的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧　裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　振作点　裘可拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你　昨天的事一点都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天？　什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个　我能把甜点也吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　要吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！我藏起来的虎猫屋的高级羊羹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说只剩下一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　非常好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不怎么吃东西也没事的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人是别人　人家是人家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是别人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以吃这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为吃到好吃的　就会有幸福的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你这样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不讨厌看你吃东西的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉酱变回以前的样子了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是这样好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再给你个巧克力～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘草君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的裘可拉同学到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉　啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是一时的记忆丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微受了点刺激就变回原样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实却正好相反啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是解释反而会变麻烦　还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此　甘草君晚上的刺激疗法很有效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔的想法吗　我什么也没做！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然差点被做了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不侧露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极短紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就算是穿运动短裤也会露点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个　太丢人了快停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把前几天对抗赛的奖品拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水银河招待券？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得这里是泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　招待胜利了的“五黑”队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了　小甘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池也就是说　泳　泳衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就期待着在泳池里发生有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池里能吃流水素面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用UOG的技术的话　可以弄个超快速的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游王子会哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣又不是内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裘可拉的事情等等　虽然遇上了好多事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是少见的没有出现脑残的绝对选项
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神也差不多把捏他用完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.45,0:24:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底变态到什么程度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经超越了恶心的范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家觉得脑内喜剧第八话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是Afilia　Saga
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然今天的主角是裘可拉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格完全变了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉的好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是奏还是觉得贪吃的裘可拉好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来　各种谜团越来越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的脑内喜剧是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有三个选项　好困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.57,0:24:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以　下周也　敬请期待

